author: mwomack
msg: Expanded test case 1 (plugin usage in defautl repository), added test case 2 (plugin usage with multiple repositories).

author: mwomack
msg: Switched Hashtable to HashMap to avoid extra synchronization. It also allows a null value for the key so the code does not need to be as paranoid about the plugin name being null.

author: mwomack
msg: Removed behavior of returning the default repository if none set.  PluginRegistry now sets this when plugin started.

author: mwomack
msg: Switched listener lists from Vector to ArrayList to avoid some unneeded synchronization charges.
Thread safety changes.  Added synchronization for listener lists when adding/removing and copying when reporting events.
